GSD.product_version: versions from v5.15 to before v6.0.10
GSD.description:
tracing: Fix race where eprobes can be called before the event

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v6.0.10 by commit 73f5191467ffe3af82f27fe0ea6a8c2fac724d3f, it was introduced in version v5.15 by commit 7491e2c442781a1860181adb5ab472a52075f393. For more details please see the references link.
